Package: libdsam2.8-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), autotools-dev, cdbs,
 libdsam2.8 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libwxgtk2.8-dev (>= 2.8.0),
 libsndfile1-dev (>= 1.0.12),
 libfftw3-dev (>= 3.0.0),
 portaudio19-dev (>= 19+svn20090620-2~)
Description: Development System for Auditory Modelling: Development package 
 DSAM is a library to support programmers producing auditory models.  It includes
 a wide collection of established and experimental auditory models.  It also
 provides facilities for reading and writing to sound file formats, in addition
 to including many analysis functions.


